long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Step into a realm of wonder and imagination every time you open a new tab. The Mystic Universe Tab brings your browser to life with an enchanting artwork of a glowing celestial sphere floating above an ancient book, surrounded by a mystical cosmic aura. Perfect for dreamers, storytellers, and explorers of the unknown, this background transforms your browsing experience into a gateway to magical worlds.

Key features:
- Beautiful background.
- Quick access to frequently visited sites.
- Real-time weather display and clock.
- News
